In [13]:
# One thing to keep in mind when casting integers from one type to another is to range allowed for the operation
# We can change to type only when the number is in the allowed range
# 8 bit –128 - 127
# 16 bit –32768 - 32767
# 32 bit –2147483648 - 2147483647
# 64 bit –2^63 - 2^63 - 1
